OL,3,CTerminal cancer patient says donating
OL,4,Ccorneas will leave a 'legacy'
OL,6,FA cancer patient given just months to
OL,7,Flive says she plans to leave her
OL,8,Fcorneas as a lasting "legacy"
OL,9,Ffollowing a campaign by a hospice to
OL,10,Frecruit more donors.
OL,12,FMargaret Wroe, of Sherburn in Elmet,
OL,13,FNorth Yorkshire, signed up to the
OL,14,Forgan donor register after St
OL,15,FLeonard's Hospice in York started
OL,16,Fencouraging patients to discuss the
OL,17,Fidea with loved ones.
