OL,3,CTerminal cancer patient says donating
OL,4,Ccorneas will leave a 'legacy'
OL,6,FMrs Wroe was diagnosed with pancreatic
OL,7,Fcancer two years ago and, after
OL,8,Fseveral rounds of chemotherapy and
OL,9,Fradiotherapy, was given just months to
OL,10,Flive.
OL,12,FShe said: "I just live everyday as it
OL,13,Fcomes because I can't change what is
OL,14,Fgoing to happen. I just live with it.
OL,16,F"It's the best feeling in the world to
OL,17,Fknow that I can do this and give my
OL,18,Fsight to someone else to see what I
OL,19,Fhave seen.
OL,21,F"I will have left a legacy."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
