OL,3,CTerminal cancer patient says donating
OL,4,Ccorneas will leave a 'legacy'
OL,6,FJust 1% of people who die in the UK
OL,7,Feach year are eligible for solid organ
OL,8,Fdonation, like kidney, liver or heart.
OL,10,FIn contrast, tissue and eye donation,
OL,11,Fincluding corneas, can be an option
OL,12,Ffor many more including people who
OL,13,Fhave had poor eyesight or some cancers.
OL,15,FNHS Blood and Transplant says up to 10
OL,16,Fpeople can benefit from a single donor.
OL,18,FMrs Wroe's husband Geoff said knowing
OL,19,Fher organs could help others would
OL,20,Fhelp him following her death.
