OL,3,CTerminal cancer patient says donating
OL,4,Ccorneas will leave a 'legacy'
OL,6,F"There's a real shortage of donors and
OL,7,Fgiving the gift of sight to someone
OL,8,Felse can be amazing."
OL,10,FLast year, more than 3,500 people in
OL,11,FEngland had their sight restored
OL,12,Fthrough corneal transplants, including
OL,13,F376 in Yorkshire and the North East.
OL,15,FBut more than 10% of organ donors opt
OL,16,Fout of leaving their eyes.
OL,18,FChris Cole, a gardener living in
OL,19,FLeeds, says his corneal transplants
OL,20,Fhad changed his life.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
