OL,3,CTerminal cancer patient says donating
OL,4,Ccorneas will leave a 'legacy'
OL,6,FHe was 14-years-old when he noticed
OL,7,Fhis vision was deteriorating and after
OL,8,Fvisiting an optician.
OL,10,FAfter unsuccessfully trying hard
OL,11,Fcontact lenses, he was placed on the
OL,12,Fwaiting list for a cornea transplant.
OL,14,FNow 34, Mr Cole said: "I wasn't able
OL,15,Fto cross roads without asking my
OL,16,Ffamily members to come and help. I
OL,17,Fused to go and watch football or
OL,18,Frugby, which was all well and good,
OL,19,Fbut I couldn't see the other side of
OL,20,Fthe pitch."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
