OL,3,CTerminal cancer patient says donating
OL,4,Ccorneas will leave a 'legacy'
OL,6,FHaving now fully recovered from both
OL,7,Fof his corneal transplants, the father-
OL,8,Fof-one says he thinks about his donors
OL,9,Falmost every day.
OL,11,F"For me I was waiting for someone to
OL,12,Fdie and I will never forget that," he
OL,13,Fsaid. "I will never know who my donors
OL,14,Fare but I see it as a thing where I
OL,15,Fshould live for them now."
